conversation-text:
Ward: Why was I pulled out of Paris?
Hill: That you'll have to ask Agent Coulson.
Ward: [over sad music] Uh, yeah. I'm Clearance Level Six. I know that Agent Coulson was killed in action before the Battle of New York. Got the full report.
Coulson: [stepping out from shadows as music suddenly revs up] Welcome to level seven.
Coulson: [grinning] Sorry, that corner was really dark and I couldn't help myself. I think there's a bulb out.
